1
00:01:49,060 --> 00:01:54,580
=Eight Hundred=

2
00:01:57,780 --> 00:01:59,750
Hui, look. We've reached Mr. Gao's home.

3
00:01:59,750 --> 00:02:02,460
(Year 1976)

4
00:02:04,390 --> 00:02:05,910
How come no Spring Couplets are posted?

5
00:02:05,910 --> 00:02:06,860
I know, right?

6
00:02:09,390 --> 00:02:10,270
Who is it?

7
00:02:10,270 --> 00:02:11,550
It's me, Hongbing.

8
00:02:15,000 --> 00:02:17,390
- You haven't even put up couplets.
- Happy Chinese New Year!

9
00:02:17,390 --> 00:02:18,740
Come in.

10
00:02:18,740 --> 00:02:19,700
What's going on?

11
00:02:20,460 --> 00:02:21,300
Come in.

12
00:02:25,350 --> 00:02:26,620
Hey,

13
00:02:26,620 --> 00:02:27,510
come out.

14
00:02:27,510 --> 00:02:28,670
It's Hongbing and his family.

15
00:02:28,670 --> 00:02:29,510
It's fine.

16
00:02:32,740 --> 00:02:33,610
Mrs. Gao.

17
00:02:33,610 --> 00:02:34,590
- Well...
- Mrs. Gao.

18
00:02:35,990 --> 00:02:36,900
Where

19
00:02:36,900 --> 00:02:38,020
did this child come from?

20
00:02:38,020 --> 00:02:39,110
I found her.

21
00:02:39,110 --> 00:02:40,300
Found her?

22
00:02:40,300 --> 00:02:41,270
Early this morning,

23
00:02:41,270 --> 00:02:42,700
I found her by the restroom entrance.

24
00:02:43,320 --> 00:02:44,180
Let me see.

25
00:02:44,180 --> 00:02:45,070
Come here.

26
00:02:47,580 --> 00:02:48,950
Is it a boy or a girl?

27
00:02:48,950 --> 00:02:50,140
It's a girl.

28
00:02:50,950 --> 00:02:51,900
Look at her face.

29
00:02:51,900 --> 00:02:52,950
Hongbing,

30
00:02:52,950 --> 00:02:54,700
since Gao Ying is gone,

31
00:02:54,700 --> 00:02:56,300
we have discussed it.

32
00:02:56,950 --> 00:02:58,830
We plan to adopt this child.

33
00:02:58,830 --> 00:02:59,670
Adopt?

34
00:03:00,350 --> 00:03:03,230
Mr. Gao, for an adoption,
you have to notify the police station.

35
00:03:03,230 --> 00:03:04,070
Of course.

36
00:03:04,350 --> 00:03:05,230
You must

37
00:03:05,230 --> 00:03:06,270
support us.

38
00:03:06,270 --> 00:03:07,110
Yes, Hongbing.

39
00:03:07,110 --> 00:03:09,140
If it's not against regulations,
I will help you.

40
00:03:09,140 --> 00:03:10,050
Hui,

41
00:03:10,050 --> 00:03:11,990
come and look at your sister.

42
00:03:11,990 --> 00:03:13,020
Take a look.

43
00:03:16,070 --> 00:03:17,420
Little girl.

44
00:03:19,220 --> 00:03:20,950
What is her relationship
to the head of the household?

45
00:03:20,950 --> 00:03:21,790
My granddaughter.

46
00:03:21,790 --> 00:03:22,680
Grandfather and granddaughter, right?

47
00:03:22,680 --> 00:03:23,530
Yes.

48
00:03:24,900 --> 00:03:25,990
What is her name?

49
00:03:25,990 --> 00:03:26,830
Mr. Gao,

50
00:03:27,460 --> 00:03:28,550
let's call her Songge.

51
00:03:28,550 --> 00:03:29,670
Gao Songge.

52
00:03:29,670 --> 00:03:31,740
It's from Gao Ying's favorite essay,

53
00:03:31,740 --> 00:03:33,620
"The Character of the Pine." How's that?

54
00:03:33,620 --> 00:03:34,620
Gao Songge. That's a good name.

55
00:03:34,620 --> 00:03:35,460
Let's go with Songge.

56
00:03:35,470 --> 00:03:36,990
(Permanent Residence Registration: Gao Songge)
Gao Songge, then.

57
00:03:36,990 --> 00:03:37,900
It's a fine name.

58
00:03:38,780 --> 00:03:42,580
=Episode 2=
(Tube Popsicle)

59
00:03:58,020 --> 00:03:59,740
These are
the empty bottles from last time.

60
00:03:59,740 --> 00:04:00,830
Count them.

61
00:04:08,390 --> 00:04:09,230
Hello?

62
00:04:09,460 --> 00:04:10,700
My dad found out.

63
00:04:10,700 --> 00:04:11,900
Stop the deal.

64
00:04:13,510 --> 00:04:14,460
Understood.

65
00:04:18,150 --> 00:04:19,420
I can't get the goods today.

66
00:04:19,420 --> 00:04:20,590
Go back and wait for my word.

67
00:04:20,590 --> 00:04:21,430
What's wrong?

68
00:04:22,270 --> 00:04:23,820
Wait. Why can't we get the goods today?

69
00:04:23,820 --> 00:04:24,660
Get out of the way.

70
00:04:25,350 --> 00:04:26,420
- Don't.
- Move.

71
00:04:26,420 --> 00:04:27,940
Just give me two bottles first, okay?

72
00:04:27,940 --> 00:04:28,790
Just two.

73
00:04:28,800 --> 00:04:29,740
I really can't take it anymore.

74
00:04:29,740 --> 00:04:30,580
Are you hooked?

75
00:04:32,060 --> 00:04:32,900
No.

76
00:04:33,230 --> 00:04:34,070
I'm not.

77
00:04:34,420 --> 00:04:35,910
Have you forgotten what the rules are?

78
00:04:37,120 --> 00:04:38,470
I saw how energized
they were after drinking it,

79
00:04:38,470 --> 00:04:39,860
so I couldn't resist having a bottle.

80
00:04:39,860 --> 00:04:41,350
I'll never drink it again, okay?

81
00:04:41,350 --> 00:04:42,200
You broke the rules.

82
00:04:42,200 --> 00:04:43,060
There is no next time.

83
00:04:43,460 --> 00:04:44,300
No way.

84
00:04:44,300 --> 00:04:45,380
Give me two bottles.

85
00:04:48,820 --> 00:04:49,710
Give them to me.

86
00:04:50,380 --> 00:04:51,230
Give them to me!

87
00:04:52,350 --> 00:04:53,300
Let go!

88
00:04:53,300 --> 00:04:54,140
Give them to me!

89
00:04:55,350 --> 00:04:56,190
Let go!

90
00:05:02,060 --> 00:05:02,900
Let go!

91
00:05:03,380 --> 00:05:04,220
Give them to me!

92
00:05:16,420 --> 00:05:17,260
Stop!

93
00:05:19,300 --> 00:05:20,140
A detonator?

94
00:05:20,380 --> 00:05:21,220
Go ahead.

95
00:05:21,590 --> 00:05:22,430
Light it.

96
00:05:24,860 --> 00:05:25,700
Are you crazy?

97
00:05:26,110 --> 00:05:27,620
I'm not afraid of doing this job.

98
00:05:28,740 --> 00:05:31,060
If you dare come any closer,
we'll both be done together!

99
00:05:34,420 --> 00:05:35,870
Just calm down first. Fine.

100
00:05:36,110 --> 00:05:37,030
You're insane.

101
00:05:37,030 --> 00:05:37,910
Crazy woman.

102
00:06:08,340 --> 00:06:10,020
(Starlight Video Hall, Rose Ballroom)

103
00:06:24,990 --> 00:06:25,940
Songge,

104
00:06:25,940 --> 00:06:27,150
where are you?

105
00:06:27,150 --> 00:06:28,180
Hui,

106
00:06:29,110 --> 00:06:30,500
my vascular fistula ruptured.

107
00:06:31,260 --> 00:06:32,670
I can't stop the bleeding.

108
00:06:33,590 --> 00:06:34,860
Can you ride your motorcycle now?

109
00:06:34,860 --> 00:06:36,230
I can make it now,

110
00:06:36,230 --> 00:06:38,260
but I won't make it
to the municipal hospital.

111
00:06:38,260 --> 00:06:39,210
Go to the mine hospital.

112
00:06:39,470 --> 00:06:40,320
No,

113
00:06:40,350 --> 00:06:41,370
go straight to my mom's.

114
00:06:41,590 --> 00:06:42,430
Now!

115
00:06:42,990 --> 00:06:45,260
What should I say when I see her?

116
00:06:45,260 --> 00:06:46,620
Just say you were hit by a car.

117
00:06:46,620 --> 00:06:47,710
Ditch your phone and your bag.

118
00:06:47,710 --> 00:06:49,110
Hide the motorcycle
in the drainage ditch.

119
00:06:49,110 --> 00:06:50,420
I'll meet you at my mom's place.

120
00:06:50,420 --> 00:06:51,260
Hurry!

121
00:06:51,860 --> 00:06:52,700
Okay.

122
00:06:55,460 --> 00:06:56,980
(Ding Yue Clinic)

123
00:06:56,990 --> 00:06:57,830
Yue,

124
00:06:58,380 --> 00:07:00,110
Hui and Songge

125
00:07:00,110 --> 00:07:02,060
grew up together.

126
00:07:02,060 --> 00:07:05,380
In my views, nowadays when young people
get into a relationship,

127
00:07:05,380 --> 00:07:07,420
they go all in like
there's no turning back.

128
00:07:10,550 --> 00:07:12,350
Back then,
to marry Hongbing, you...

129
00:07:12,350 --> 00:07:13,500
Wait.

130
00:07:13,780 --> 00:07:14,910
We were talking about my son.

131
00:07:14,910 --> 00:07:16,060
Why bring me into it?

132
00:07:16,590 --> 00:07:17,740
I mean

133
00:07:17,740 --> 00:07:20,710
it's not enough just to talk to Hui.

134
00:07:20,710 --> 00:07:22,150
You have to discuss it with Songge.

135
00:07:25,260 --> 00:07:26,860
That's not appropriate.

136
00:07:26,860 --> 00:07:28,590
Don't be so blunt with her.

137
00:07:29,940 --> 00:07:30,820
Xi,

138
00:07:30,820 --> 00:07:31,670
give me some fruit.

139
00:07:31,670 --> 00:07:32,510
Okay.

140
00:07:54,580 --> 00:07:55,980
(Ding Yue Clinic)

141
00:08:44,620 --> 00:08:45,620
What happened to her?

142
00:08:48,140 --> 00:08:48,980
Songge!

143
00:08:49,780 --> 00:08:50,620
Songge!

144
00:08:50,990 --> 00:08:51,830
Songge!

145
00:08:52,110 --> 00:08:52,950
What's going on?

146
00:08:52,950 --> 00:08:53,950
Songge, what happened?

147
00:08:53,950 --> 00:08:55,020
Why is there so much blood?

148
00:08:55,430 --> 00:08:56,860
- Poor girl.
- Songge.

149
00:08:56,990 --> 00:08:58,830
- Songge.
- Songge.

150
00:09:03,020 --> 00:09:04,710
Songge, you're in bad state.

151
00:09:04,710 --> 00:09:05,860
Why didn't you go to the hospital?

152
00:09:05,860 --> 00:09:07,620
You know what kind of
conditions this clinic has.

153
00:09:07,620 --> 00:09:08,500
Stop nagging.

154
00:09:08,500 --> 00:09:09,390
She's my child.

155
00:09:09,390 --> 00:09:10,470
If something's wrong,
who else would she turn to?

156
00:09:10,470 --> 00:09:11,410
Quick, get the scissors!

157
00:09:11,430 --> 00:09:12,320
Stop it.

158
00:09:13,230 --> 00:09:14,070
I'll take a call.

159
00:09:15,700 --> 00:09:16,570
Hello?

160
00:09:17,310 --> 00:09:18,150
Hongbing.

161
00:09:18,830 --> 00:09:20,430
Songge's vascular fistula ruptured.

162
00:09:20,430 --> 00:09:21,830
Get a car over here immediately.

163
00:09:21,830 --> 00:09:23,110
We need to get her
to the municipal hospital.

164
00:09:23,110 --> 00:09:24,230
- It's okay, Songge.
- Hurry up!

165
00:09:24,230 --> 00:09:25,070
I have to go.

166
00:09:25,780 --> 00:09:26,900
Hand me the scissors, quick!

167
00:09:26,900 --> 00:09:27,990
Coming.

168
00:09:28,540 --> 00:09:29,430
Mom,

169
00:09:29,440 --> 00:09:30,660
I bought some fruit for you.

170
00:09:33,140 --> 00:09:34,140
What's happening?

171
00:09:34,140 --> 00:09:35,500
- Songge.
- Her fistula ruptured.

172
00:09:35,500 --> 00:09:36,410
Don't worry, Hui.

173
00:09:36,410 --> 00:09:37,260
Your dad has already called for a car.

174
00:09:37,260 --> 00:09:38,230
It'll be here soon.

175
00:09:43,230 --> 00:09:44,070
Come on, quick!

176
00:09:44,070 --> 00:09:45,110
- Hurry!
- The car is here.

177
00:09:45,260 --> 00:09:46,500
Quick, the car is here!

178
00:09:46,500 --> 00:09:47,590
She's lost so much blood.

179
00:09:47,590 --> 00:09:49,070
Hurry up!

180
00:09:49,070 --> 00:09:50,020
Hang in there, Songge.

181
00:09:50,020 --> 00:09:51,660
- Come.
- Okay.

182
00:09:51,660 --> 00:09:53,140
Open the car door.

183
00:09:56,760 --> 00:09:57,660
Hui.

184
00:09:57,660 --> 00:09:58,620
Hurry up!

185
00:09:58,620 --> 00:09:59,460
Okay.

186
00:09:59,740 --> 00:10:00,590
Go to the other side.

187
00:10:00,590 --> 00:10:01,430
I'll handle this.

188
00:10:15,540 --> 00:10:18,180
(Jiangbin Municipal People's Hospital)

189
00:10:19,660 --> 00:10:20,570
Slow down.

190
00:10:20,590 --> 00:10:21,430
Quick.

191
00:10:21,900 --> 00:10:22,780
Mom, hold her.

192
00:10:22,780 --> 00:10:23,620
I'm going to get a bag.

193
00:10:23,620 --> 00:10:24,610
Okay.

194
00:10:25,620 --> 00:10:26,500
Don't pull so hard.

195
00:10:26,500 --> 00:10:27,540
Let me help you.

196
00:10:28,990 --> 00:10:29,830
Look at you.

197
00:10:31,740 --> 00:10:33,860
What's the big rush?

198
00:10:37,780 --> 00:10:41,260
(Emergency Resuscitation Room)

199
00:10:44,540 --> 00:10:45,540
You must be hungry.

200
00:10:50,380 --> 00:10:51,310
Aren't you going in?

201
00:10:52,190 --> 00:10:53,830
Songge fell asleep inside.

202
00:10:57,500 --> 00:10:59,230
This poor child.

203
00:11:00,020 --> 00:11:02,140
She has to get another vascular shunt.

204
00:11:02,140 --> 00:11:03,430
Fortunately,

205
00:11:03,430 --> 00:11:04,710
everything is fine now.

206
00:11:07,230 --> 00:11:08,990
It breaks my heart to see her.

207
00:11:10,070 --> 00:11:11,230
What's gonna happen

208
00:11:12,070 --> 00:11:13,350
to her in the future?

209
00:11:16,950 --> 00:11:18,470
I asked you to talk to Hui.

210
00:11:19,110 --> 00:11:19,950
Did you?

211
00:11:19,950 --> 00:11:21,140
Of course I did.

212
00:11:21,140 --> 00:11:22,900
I told him this morning.

213
00:11:22,900 --> 00:11:24,140
What did he say?

214
00:11:24,140 --> 00:11:26,070
What could he say?

215
00:11:26,070 --> 00:11:27,430
He has grown up, after all.

216
00:11:27,430 --> 00:11:29,140
I feel like

217
00:11:29,140 --> 00:11:30,260
we should stay out

218
00:11:30,260 --> 00:11:31,740
of his business.

219
00:11:34,190 --> 00:11:35,830
You're really something.

220
00:11:35,830 --> 00:11:37,540
I asked you to talk to Hui,

221
00:11:37,540 --> 00:11:39,260
but instead, he talked you out of it.

222
00:11:39,260 --> 00:11:41,260
How can you be so useless?

223
00:11:41,260 --> 00:11:42,500
You can't even handle him.

224
00:11:42,500 --> 00:11:43,540
You're making me furious.

225
00:11:43,540 --> 00:11:44,500
What are you doing?

226
00:11:45,110 --> 00:11:45,950
Well,

227
00:11:45,950 --> 00:11:47,380
if you're so capable, you go.

228
00:11:47,380 --> 00:11:49,660
Why do you keep pressuring me?

229
00:11:49,660 --> 00:11:51,620
Aren't you the head of the family?

230
00:11:51,620 --> 00:11:52,530
Must I handle

231
00:11:52,540 --> 00:11:53,660
every family crisis for you?

232
00:11:53,660 --> 00:11:55,190
I've already told Hui.

233
00:11:55,190 --> 00:11:56,740
What can I do if he won't break up?

234
00:11:56,740 --> 00:11:58,470
Then talk to him again.

235
00:11:58,470 --> 00:11:59,590
Until he agrees.

236
00:11:59,590 --> 00:12:00,430
Stop it.

237
00:12:00,440 --> 00:12:01,590
Others might see us.

238
00:12:01,590 --> 00:12:02,590
What are you doing?

239
00:12:04,310 --> 00:12:05,470
Hui went to buy water

240
00:12:05,470 --> 00:12:08,260
and hasn't come back yet. I'll go check.

241
00:12:08,260 --> 00:12:09,110
Hongbing,

242
00:12:09,110 --> 00:12:10,070
why are you hiding?

243
00:12:20,740 --> 00:12:22,020
The trunk is broken.

244
00:12:23,540 --> 00:12:24,380
I'm sorry.

245
00:12:25,310 --> 00:12:27,830
I've gotten so much blood in your car.

246
00:12:27,830 --> 00:12:28,710
How much

247
00:12:28,710 --> 00:12:29,990
for a cleaning?

248
00:12:29,990 --> 00:12:30,830
Don't worry about it.

249
00:12:31,230 --> 00:12:32,070
I can't do that.

250
00:12:32,950 --> 00:12:34,900
You've taken good care
of me all these years.

251
00:12:34,900 --> 00:12:36,860
But I really can't help
with Gao Ying's case.

252
00:12:36,860 --> 00:12:38,350
That's a separate issue.

253
00:12:38,350 --> 00:12:39,950
Here, take it. This is all I have.

254
00:12:39,950 --> 00:12:41,020
I don't want your money.

255
00:12:41,020 --> 00:12:42,110
I said I don't want it.

256
00:12:55,990 --> 00:12:57,140
What happened to your trunk?

257
00:12:58,020 --> 00:12:59,020
Ask Hui.

258
00:12:59,860 --> 00:13:01,070
I told him not to pull it

259
00:13:01,070 --> 00:13:01,910
and I'd open it.

260
00:13:01,920 --> 00:13:03,590
But he wouldn't listen and
insist on that bag.

261
00:13:03,590 --> 00:13:05,310
I don't know what his rush was.

262
00:13:05,310 --> 00:13:06,150
Well.

263
00:13:09,470 --> 00:13:11,540
Hui, hurry up!

264
00:13:15,220 --> 00:13:16,070
Mom, hold her.

265
00:13:16,070 --> 00:13:17,190
I'm going to get a bag.

266
00:13:17,190 --> 00:13:18,590
Hui, hurry up!

267
00:13:18,590 --> 00:13:19,780
I told him not to pull it,

268
00:13:19,780 --> 00:13:20,640
and I'd open it.

269
00:13:20,650 --> 00:13:22,500
But he wouldn't listen and
insist on that bag.

270
00:13:44,140 --> 00:13:44,980
Dad,

271
00:14:02,780 --> 00:14:04,020
where were you just now?

272
00:14:05,860 --> 00:14:07,500
I just called Han Ning.

273
00:14:07,500 --> 00:14:08,990
I told her not to open the shop tonight

274
00:14:08,990 --> 00:14:10,660
and to go home to look after Grandpa.

275
00:14:19,020 --> 00:14:19,900
Songge.

276
00:14:21,260 --> 00:14:22,310
I...

277
00:14:23,660 --> 00:14:24,990
I want to ask you something.

278
00:14:25,710 --> 00:14:26,780
What is it?

279
00:14:27,620 --> 00:14:29,190
All these years,

280
00:14:30,260 --> 00:14:31,470
we

281
00:14:33,380 --> 00:14:34,740
have been good to you, right?

282
00:14:35,380 --> 00:14:37,350
If it weren't for you and Mr. Chen,

283
00:14:38,020 --> 00:14:39,140
I would have died long ago.

284
00:14:39,830 --> 00:14:41,350
Then, I'll just

285
00:14:43,020 --> 00:14:44,260
speak plainly.

286
00:14:47,540 --> 00:14:48,380
Can

287
00:14:50,830 --> 00:14:52,470
you leave Hui?

288
00:15:07,380 --> 00:15:09,110
You bought so many drinks.

289
00:15:09,110 --> 00:15:10,050
Can you finish them all?

290
00:15:10,720 --> 00:15:12,240
Songge is staying for a couple of days.

291
00:15:12,780 --> 00:15:13,950
She doesn't drink much,

292
00:15:13,950 --> 00:15:14,790
but I do.

293
00:15:17,950 --> 00:15:19,190
This bag is so dirty.

294
00:15:20,780 --> 00:15:22,230
Why is there blood on it?

295
00:15:24,950 --> 00:15:25,990
It might be from

296
00:15:25,990 --> 00:15:27,590
Songge's injury.

297
00:15:28,470 --> 00:15:29,590
I didn't notice.

298
00:15:38,350 --> 00:15:39,590
Songge,

299
00:15:41,500 --> 00:15:42,660
it's really not

300
00:15:42,660 --> 00:15:43,950
that I look down on you.

301
00:15:46,110 --> 00:15:47,310
Mr. Chen and I

302
00:15:48,140 --> 00:15:50,070
won't be with Hui forever.

303
00:15:50,070 --> 00:15:51,190
If Hui has to carry

304
00:15:51,190 --> 00:15:52,990
such a heavy burden alone,

305
00:15:52,990 --> 00:15:53,950
we

306
00:15:54,470 --> 00:15:55,470
won't be able

307
00:15:55,470 --> 00:15:56,990
to rest in peace.

308
00:16:00,190 --> 00:16:02,780
They say a parent's love
knows no bounds.

309
00:16:03,780 --> 00:16:05,070
Can you please

310
00:16:05,070 --> 00:16:06,590
try to understand

311
00:16:06,590 --> 00:16:08,350
my feelings?

312
00:16:12,110 --> 00:16:13,070
Songge.

313
00:16:14,260 --> 00:16:15,100
Mom.

314
00:16:20,540 --> 00:16:21,380
How is Songge?

315
00:16:28,780 --> 00:16:30,110
How is she? Is she okay?

316
00:16:31,740 --> 00:16:33,740
It's so dirty to leave the bag there.

317
00:16:36,020 --> 00:16:36,860
Dad,

318
00:16:38,110 --> 00:16:38,990
I'll take it.

319
00:16:42,860 --> 00:16:43,860
What's inside?

320
00:16:43,860 --> 00:16:45,140
You're so nervous.

321
00:16:45,140 --> 00:16:46,080
Nothing.

322
00:16:46,090 --> 00:16:47,260
Can I take a look?

323
00:16:47,260 --> 00:16:48,350
No.

324
00:16:49,620 --> 00:16:50,830
What are you hiding in there?

325
00:16:50,830 --> 00:16:51,950
I'm not hiding anything.

326
00:16:51,950 --> 00:16:53,540
Dad, why do you want to see my stuff?

327
00:16:53,540 --> 00:16:55,110
What are you arguing about?

328
00:16:55,110 --> 00:16:56,710
Songge is trying to rest.

329
00:16:57,820 --> 00:16:58,900
What if I insist on seeing it?

330
00:16:58,900 --> 00:16:59,740
No way.

331
00:17:00,260 --> 00:17:01,380
You can't look at my things.

332
00:17:01,380 --> 00:17:02,220
No, Dad.

333
00:17:02,230 --> 00:17:03,830
Dad, you can't look. No.

334
00:17:03,830 --> 00:17:05,230
- You can't, Dad.
- Stop it.

335
00:17:05,230 --> 00:17:07,470
- Dad, you can't.
- What are you doing?

336
00:17:07,470 --> 00:17:08,310
Dad!

337
00:17:09,460 --> 00:17:14,940
(Condoms)

338
00:17:32,710 --> 00:17:35,470
With so many things,
are you planning to open a shop?

339
00:17:51,470 --> 00:17:52,910
Yue,

340
00:17:53,710 --> 00:17:54,550
Yue.

341
00:17:54,820 --> 00:17:56,470
What are you doing?

342
00:17:56,470 --> 00:17:58,390
Why were you
snooping through his things?

343
00:17:58,390 --> 00:17:59,990
I thought it was some adult tapes.

344
00:17:59,990 --> 00:18:01,870
- You know?
- Hui is so disappointing.

345
00:18:01,870 --> 00:18:04,100
She's in bad state
and I talked such things to her.

346
00:18:04,100 --> 00:18:05,470
Am I ruthless?

347
00:18:05,470 --> 00:18:06,540
Don't worry about them.

348
00:18:06,540 --> 00:18:07,580
Just take it slow, okay?

349
00:18:07,580 --> 00:18:08,500
What do you mean by slow?

350
00:18:08,500 --> 00:18:09,440
How can we take it slow?

351
00:18:14,060 --> 00:18:15,190
I have to go to the station.

352
00:18:15,190 --> 00:18:16,300
Go home by yourself.

353
00:18:16,870 --> 00:18:18,150
I haven't even finished talking.

354
00:18:18,150 --> 00:18:19,820
Be safe on the road.

355
00:18:19,820 --> 00:18:21,300
I haven't finished talking.

356
00:18:30,540 --> 00:18:32,710
I'm sorry.

357
00:18:34,820 --> 00:18:35,740
That scared me.

358
00:18:36,710 --> 00:18:37,910
That was too dangerous.

359
00:18:38,670 --> 00:18:40,190
From now on,

360
00:18:40,190 --> 00:18:41,150
I'll handle deals.

361
00:18:43,430 --> 00:18:44,290
What are you saying?

362
00:18:44,400 --> 00:18:46,340
Didn't we agree on this?

363
00:18:46,340 --> 00:18:47,870
I'll handle the deals,

364
00:18:47,870 --> 00:18:49,540
and you're in charge
of getting the stock.

365
00:18:50,190 --> 00:18:51,820
Isn't this the first time

366
00:18:51,820 --> 00:18:53,580
something like this has happened?

367
00:18:53,580 --> 00:18:54,710
You know

368
00:18:55,900 --> 00:18:57,360
that I don't want to hide behind you.

369
00:18:58,000 --> 00:18:59,430
Otherwise, I'd feel even more guilty.

370
00:18:59,990 --> 00:19:02,060
But if this happens again,

371
00:19:02,060 --> 00:19:03,540
- I...
- Don't think about it.

372
00:19:03,540 --> 00:19:06,100
Isn't everything fine now?

373
00:19:06,100 --> 00:19:08,150
We set the rules together.

374
00:19:09,430 --> 00:19:10,950
No one is allowed to break them.

375
00:19:10,950 --> 00:19:12,060
If you break them,

376
00:19:12,890 --> 00:19:14,430
I won't continue the treatment anymore.

377
00:19:15,820 --> 00:19:17,390
- But...
- No buts.

378
00:19:22,340 --> 00:19:23,230
By the way,

379
00:19:24,500 --> 00:19:25,470
where's the bag?

380
00:19:26,340 --> 00:19:28,300
Didn't I tell you to throw it all away?

381
00:19:28,300 --> 00:19:29,430
Why did you bring it back?

382
00:19:31,230 --> 00:19:33,020
It was stained with my blood.

383
00:19:33,620 --> 00:19:35,020
I was afraid something would happen.

384
00:19:35,950 --> 00:19:37,020
Don't worry.

385
00:19:37,020 --> 00:19:37,950
I hid it.

386
00:19:38,430 --> 00:19:40,910
When there are fewer people outside,
I'll go get it back.

387
00:20:16,980 --> 00:20:18,960
♪Forsaking my ideals♪

388
00:20:19,180 --> 00:20:22,340
♪Anyone can do that♪

389
00:20:23,190 --> 00:20:27,140
♪What's there to fear
if one day it's just you and me?♪

390
00:20:28,430 --> 00:20:30,190
I hope you have a great time tonight.

391
00:20:30,710 --> 00:20:32,710
- Hey, where are you from?
- Jiangbin.

392
00:20:32,710 --> 00:20:34,020
What are you doing?

393
00:20:34,020 --> 00:20:35,910
Trying to get my friend drunk
while I was away?

394
00:20:35,910 --> 00:20:36,870
Move over.

395
00:20:36,870 --> 00:20:37,710
I wasn't.

396
00:20:37,910 --> 00:20:39,300
They came all the way to Fengyang,

397
00:20:39,300 --> 00:20:40,540
so we have to treat them well.

398
00:20:40,540 --> 00:20:41,620
- Enjoy it.
- Enjoy it.

399
00:20:41,990 --> 00:20:42,950
Nobody move.

400
00:20:42,950 --> 00:20:43,950
Turn on the lights.

401
00:20:43,950 --> 00:20:45,380
- Police inspection.
- Don't move!

402
00:20:45,630 --> 00:20:46,470
Mr. Kang,

403
00:20:46,470 --> 00:20:48,100
what's going on?

404
00:20:48,100 --> 00:20:50,020
We received a report
that someone is using contraband here.

405
00:20:50,020 --> 00:20:51,060
Why wasn't there a notice?

406
00:20:51,330 --> 00:20:53,150
If I notified you,
what would I be inspecting?

407
00:20:53,150 --> 00:20:54,400
You know the public security regulations.

408
00:20:54,400 --> 00:20:55,270
Cooperate with us.

409
00:20:55,270 --> 00:20:56,540
We'll cooperate, absolutely.

410
00:20:56,540 --> 00:20:57,670
Men on the left.

411
00:20:57,670 --> 00:20:58,780
Women on the right.

412
00:20:58,780 --> 00:21:00,390
Each of you, take a cup.

413
00:21:00,390 --> 00:21:01,300
Urine test.

414
00:21:01,300 --> 00:21:02,390
No one's getting away.

415
00:21:03,670 --> 00:21:04,510
Chief Liu,

416
00:21:04,710 --> 00:21:05,570
I'm sorry.

417
00:21:05,570 --> 00:21:06,910
Something delayed me.

418
00:21:06,910 --> 00:21:07,790
It's fine.

419
00:21:07,850 --> 00:21:09,580
We also received
a report about contraband.

420
00:21:09,580 --> 00:21:10,860
We came to check
this place on short notice.

421
00:21:10,870 --> 00:21:12,300
How is it? Is the search going smoothly?

422
00:21:12,340 --> 00:21:13,200
It's okay.

423
00:21:13,200 --> 00:21:14,820
Limin is inside organizing it.

424
00:21:14,820 --> 00:21:15,740
By the way,

425
00:21:15,750 --> 00:21:17,740
the composition report on the body
came out this afternoon.

426
00:21:17,750 --> 00:21:18,820
(Welcome to Vienna)
On the victim's remains,

427
00:21:18,820 --> 00:21:20,390
some strange things were found.

428
00:21:21,380 --> 00:21:22,220
What was found?

429
00:21:22,540 --> 00:21:23,780
There is carborundum,

430
00:21:23,780 --> 00:21:25,640
as well as potassium manganate
and manganese dioxide.

431
00:21:26,660 --> 00:21:28,100
I know what carborundum is.

432
00:21:28,100 --> 00:21:29,620
It's an industrial abrasive.

433
00:21:29,620 --> 00:21:30,740
What about the other two?

434
00:21:30,740 --> 00:21:31,580
The report says they're

435
00:21:31,580 --> 00:21:33,900
byproducts of potassium permanganate
decomposition at high temperatures.

436
00:21:33,900 --> 00:21:34,900
Before the body was burned,

437
00:21:34,900 --> 00:21:36,780
there was potassium permanganate
on the victim.

438
00:21:38,820 --> 00:21:40,500
Potassium permanganate.

439
00:21:56,940 --> 00:21:57,780
You're awake?

440
00:21:58,700 --> 00:21:59,860
Where is Jiao Yuqin?

441
00:22:00,340 --> 00:22:01,180
Who are you?

442
00:22:01,900 --> 00:22:03,100
Why did you kidnap me?

443
00:22:03,100 --> 00:22:04,780
Where is Jiao Yuqin?

444
00:22:04,780 --> 00:22:05,700
I don't know Jiao Yuqin.

445
00:22:05,700 --> 00:22:06,700
Let me go!

446
00:22:08,500 --> 00:22:09,700
I'm asking you

447
00:22:09,700 --> 00:22:11,460
if you sell the cough syrup?

448
00:22:13,100 --> 00:22:14,180
What cough syrup?

449
00:22:14,860 --> 00:22:16,420
I don't know what you're talking about.

450
00:22:16,420 --> 00:22:18,300
Then what's in that bag

451
00:22:18,300 --> 00:22:19,580
you hid in the alleyway?

452
00:22:20,320 --> 00:22:22,060
The moment you
sneaked out of the hospital,

453
00:22:22,060 --> 00:22:23,380
I had my eyes on you.

454
00:22:23,380 --> 00:22:24,880
I followed you all the way to the alley.

455
00:22:25,140 --> 00:22:26,340
Stop playing dumb with me.

456
00:22:26,340 --> 00:22:27,260
Is it money you want?

457
00:22:27,260 --> 00:22:28,940
I'll give you however much you want.

458
00:22:28,940 --> 00:22:30,060
I don't want money.

459
00:22:30,700 --> 00:22:32,740
I just want to know where Jiao Yuqin is.

460
00:22:32,740 --> 00:22:34,900
I told you I don't know the person.

461
00:22:34,900 --> 00:22:36,940
I don't even know who that is.

462
00:22:36,940 --> 00:22:37,780
You won't talk?

463
00:22:38,180 --> 00:22:39,100
What are you doing?

464
00:22:41,580 --> 00:22:42,420
Where are you?

465
00:22:43,460 --> 00:22:44,980
What are you pouring on me?

466
00:22:47,140 --> 00:22:49,220
What do you want? Say something!

467
00:22:49,220 --> 00:22:51,340
I'm asking you for the last time.

468
00:22:51,340 --> 00:22:52,980
Where is Jiao Yuqin?

469
00:22:52,980 --> 00:22:54,500
I really don't know her!

470
00:22:54,500 --> 00:22:56,300
Then go to heck, you brat.

471
00:22:56,900 --> 00:22:58,140
Potassium permanganate

472
00:22:58,620 --> 00:22:59,820
and glycerol.

473
00:23:03,060 --> 00:23:05,760
Get a taste of being burned.

474
00:23:05,760 --> 00:23:06,620
Are you sick?

475
00:23:06,620 --> 00:23:07,460
Are you crazy?

476
00:23:07,980 --> 00:23:09,060
You have the wrong person.

477
00:23:09,060 --> 00:23:10,300
This must be a mistake.

478
00:23:10,300 --> 00:23:11,940
I don't know who this person
you're talking about is.

479
00:23:11,940 --> 00:23:13,980
There's no way I have the wrong person.

480
00:23:13,980 --> 00:23:15,620
You drug dealers

481
00:23:15,620 --> 00:23:17,100
never tell a word of truth.

482
00:23:17,100 --> 00:23:18,100
My wife

483
00:23:18,100 --> 00:23:19,540
was destroyed and

484
00:23:19,540 --> 00:23:20,900
deceived by you!

485
00:23:20,900 --> 00:23:22,900
I'm going to burn you!

486
00:23:23,460 --> 00:23:24,340
Huo Kaiming!

487
00:23:29,420 --> 00:23:31,140
You said
you've been following me all day.

488
00:23:31,340 --> 00:23:32,260
Aside from my parents,

489
00:23:32,260 --> 00:23:33,780
you're the only one
who followed me today.

490
00:23:33,780 --> 00:23:35,140
It's you, Huo Kaiming.

491
00:23:35,140 --> 00:23:35,980
It's you!

492
00:23:36,820 --> 00:23:37,820
Brat,

493
00:23:38,940 --> 00:23:40,540
I'll give you one last chance.

494
00:23:40,540 --> 00:23:41,460
Tell me

495
00:23:41,460 --> 00:23:42,980
where Jiao Yuqin is?

496
00:23:42,980 --> 00:23:43,900
Do you know her?

497
00:23:43,900 --> 00:23:45,340
I don't!

498
00:23:45,340 --> 00:23:46,500
If you burn me,

499
00:23:46,500 --> 00:23:48,220
my dad won't let you get away with it.

500
00:23:48,220 --> 00:23:50,260
By then, you'll be nothing but ash.

501
00:23:50,260 --> 00:23:51,940
What could your dad possibly find?

502
00:23:51,940 --> 00:23:53,900
I'm burning you right now.

503
00:24:04,100 --> 00:24:06,260
You brat, trying to be clever
with me, huh?

504
00:24:06,260 --> 00:24:07,580
You're done!

505
00:24:09,940 --> 00:24:10,940
Mr. Huo.

506
00:24:10,940 --> 00:24:11,940
Mr. Huo,

507
00:24:13,140 --> 00:24:14,820
your wife is Jiao Yuqin, right?

508
00:24:14,820 --> 00:24:16,540
Did she run off with a drug dealer?

509
00:24:16,540 --> 00:24:17,820
Nonsense, impossible!

510
00:24:17,820 --> 00:24:19,100
Yuqin isn't that kind of person.

511
00:24:19,100 --> 00:24:20,780
The drug dealers

512
00:24:20,780 --> 00:24:21,700
who coerced her!

513
00:24:21,700 --> 00:24:23,220
Darn it!

514
00:24:23,700 --> 00:24:25,020
In Fengyang,

515
00:24:25,020 --> 00:24:26,140
only I am able

516
00:24:26,140 --> 00:24:27,380
to help you find Jiao Yuqin.

517
00:24:28,020 --> 00:24:29,820
Although I don't know her,

518
00:24:29,820 --> 00:24:31,500
I know the person selling the drugs.

519
00:24:33,060 --> 00:24:35,900
Mr. Huo,

520
00:24:35,900 --> 00:24:37,260
let go of me.

521
00:24:42,000 --> 00:24:42,980
Why should I believe you?

522
00:24:43,820 --> 00:24:45,220
If I lie to you,

523
00:24:45,220 --> 00:24:46,860
you can find me anytime.

524
00:24:47,540 --> 00:24:48,660
I'll help you find her

525
00:24:48,660 --> 00:24:49,860
if you let me go.

526
00:24:53,580 --> 00:24:54,540
You brat.

527
00:24:55,580 --> 00:24:57,260
Remember what you said today.

528
00:24:57,260 --> 00:24:58,180
If you dare lie to me,

529
00:24:58,180 --> 00:24:59,500
I'll kill you whenever I want.

530
00:25:08,780 --> 00:25:09,820
That batch of goods

531
00:25:10,540 --> 00:25:11,580
stays here with me for now.

532
00:25:12,220 --> 00:25:14,270
Wait for me to find you
at the roller skating rink.

533
00:25:36,340 --> 00:25:37,340
Chen Liang?

534
00:25:37,340 --> 00:25:38,180
I'm here.

535
00:25:38,860 --> 00:25:39,700
You can go.

536
00:25:40,980 --> 00:25:41,860
Wang Sui?

537
00:25:42,500 --> 00:25:43,340
That's me.

538
00:25:45,300 --> 00:25:47,500
Tested positive for Kejianin.
Take her away.

539
00:25:47,500 --> 00:25:48,660
I didn't do anything.

540
00:25:48,660 --> 00:25:50,180
You must have made a mistake.

541
00:25:50,180 --> 00:25:51,220
She's a university student.

542
00:25:51,220 --> 00:25:52,060
She just arrived in Fengyang.

543
00:25:52,070 --> 00:25:53,540
How could she have done anything wrong?

544
00:25:53,540 --> 00:25:54,580
We won't make a mistake.

545
00:25:54,580 --> 00:25:55,740
Do not obstruct us in duty.

546
00:25:55,740 --> 00:25:56,620
Take her in.

547
00:25:56,620 --> 00:25:58,540
- Xin Yu!
- This must be a misunderstanding.

548
00:25:58,540 --> 00:25:59,500
Please check again.

549
00:25:59,500 --> 00:26:00,780
- Why are you running?
- Get out of the way!

550
00:26:00,780 --> 00:26:01,620
Don't move!

551
00:26:01,620 --> 00:26:02,460
(Welcome to Vienna)

552
00:26:03,660 --> 00:26:05,020
- Where do you think you're going?
- Where are you running?

553
00:26:05,020 --> 00:26:06,180
- Stop!
- Get down!

554
00:26:06,180 --> 00:26:08,580
Get down!

555
00:26:08,620 --> 00:26:09,740
Where are you running to?

556
00:26:09,740 --> 00:26:11,110
Where exactly do you think you're going?

557
00:26:11,210 --> 00:26:12,060
Take them down.

558
00:26:12,060 --> 00:26:12,900
Move!

559
00:26:16,300 --> 00:26:19,420
(Emergency Department, Outpatient Department,
Jiangbin Municipal People's Hospital)

560
00:26:53,060 --> 00:26:57,660
Where is Jiao Yuqin?

561
00:26:57,660 --> 00:26:59,100
Do you know Jiao Yuqin?

562
00:27:03,860 --> 00:27:05,340
Who's Jiao Yuqin?

563
00:27:13,380 --> 00:27:14,220
Hui,

564
00:27:16,620 --> 00:27:17,460
you're back.

565
00:27:18,660 --> 00:27:19,780
Did I wake you?

566
00:27:21,020 --> 00:27:22,220
I wasn't sleeping soundly.

567
00:27:23,100 --> 00:27:24,500
I was worried about you.

568
00:27:25,140 --> 00:27:26,060
How are you?

569
00:27:26,060 --> 00:27:26,930
Are you okay?

570
00:27:27,580 --> 00:27:28,460
I'm fine.

571
00:27:29,060 --> 00:27:30,460
Everything's been handled.

572
00:27:31,500 --> 00:27:33,060
Why did it take you so long?

573
00:27:33,860 --> 00:27:35,660
Did something happen?

574
00:27:36,980 --> 00:27:38,380
Nothing happened.

575
00:27:41,940 --> 00:27:43,300
Go to sleep now.

576
00:27:43,300 --> 00:27:44,300
You need to rest.

577
00:27:47,260 --> 00:27:48,420
What happened to your neck?

578
00:27:49,100 --> 00:27:50,820
It looks like you're hurt.

579
00:27:52,100 --> 00:27:52,940
No,

580
00:27:53,140 --> 00:27:54,460
it might be an allergy.

581
00:27:54,460 --> 00:27:55,300
I scratched it.

582
00:27:55,740 --> 00:27:56,940
Today,

583
00:27:56,940 --> 00:27:58,260
did my mom say something to you?

584
00:27:59,300 --> 00:28:01,020
You don't look very well.

585
00:28:03,660 --> 00:28:04,500
No.

586
00:28:06,220 --> 00:28:07,820
She just told me

587
00:28:08,460 --> 00:28:09,660
to be more careful

588
00:28:09,660 --> 00:28:10,940
when I go out in the future.

589
00:28:12,060 --> 00:28:13,220
She was just worried about me.

590
00:28:13,400 --> 00:28:14,580
She didn't say anything else?

591
00:28:16,060 --> 00:28:16,900
No.

592
00:28:18,140 --> 00:28:18,980
Just sleep.

593
00:28:34,260 --> 00:28:35,340
Hui.

594
00:28:38,340 --> 00:28:39,300
Tell me.

595
00:28:41,460 --> 00:28:43,940
If we could go back
to when we were kids,

596
00:28:45,620 --> 00:28:46,780
how wonderful would that be?

597
00:28:49,500 --> 00:28:50,940
Happy birthday, Songge.

598
00:28:51,540 --> 00:28:53,900
I hope I can eat cake every day.

599
00:28:56,240 --> 00:28:57,940
Remember to do
your homework when you get home.

600
00:28:58,340 --> 00:28:59,540
I know, Hui.

601
00:29:00,300 --> 00:29:01,140
See you tomorrow.

602
00:29:01,580 --> 00:29:02,940
See you tomorrow.

603
00:29:05,000 --> 00:29:07,340
♪So colorful and free♪

604
00:29:08,320 --> 00:29:12,580
♪Yet popping at a single touch♪

605
00:29:12,660 --> 00:29:13,540
Hui.

606
00:29:14,130 --> 00:29:14,980
Hui,

607
00:29:14,980 --> 00:29:16,460
where are you taking me?

608
00:29:16,460 --> 00:29:17,740
I'm taking you
to the roller skating rink.

609
00:29:17,740 --> 00:29:18,720
- Okay!
- Let's go.

610
00:29:21,250 --> 00:29:26,330
♪Just like when we
were innocent children♪

611
00:29:27,140 --> 00:29:28,020
I've learned!

612
00:29:28,020 --> 00:29:29,660
I'm so smart!

613
00:29:29,660 --> 00:29:30,980
Great job.

614
00:29:30,980 --> 00:29:33,460
If you can manage to skate a whole lap,
come find me again.

615
00:29:33,460 --> 00:29:34,300
In 30 minutes,

616
00:29:34,300 --> 00:29:35,140
you'll see

617
00:29:35,140 --> 00:29:36,820
an airplane right here.

618
00:29:36,820 --> 00:29:38,620
Let's fly!

619
00:29:41,780 --> 00:29:42,900
Songge.

620
00:29:42,900 --> 00:29:43,900
Chen Hui.

621
00:29:43,900 --> 00:29:47,080
♪The moonlight shines on the bed♪

622
00:29:47,780 --> 00:29:48,700
Come on.

623
00:29:50,820 --> 00:29:52,020
Let's go.

624
00:29:53,890 --> 00:29:57,620
♪Just pretend
you're holding my hand again♪

625
00:29:57,700 --> 00:29:58,580
Chen Hui,

626
00:29:58,590 --> 00:30:00,260
why do you always like coming here?

627
00:30:00,260 --> 00:30:02,940
Because I can stand high
and see far here.

628
00:30:02,940 --> 00:30:04,940
This is the highest point in Fengyang.

629
00:30:06,380 --> 00:30:07,940
What do you think? Isn't it cool?

630
00:30:08,300 --> 00:30:09,980
Cool. And this torch.

631
00:30:10,660 --> 00:30:12,060
At night,

632
00:30:12,060 --> 00:30:14,780
when all the lights in Fengyang are out,

633
00:30:14,780 --> 00:30:15,900
it will still be lit.

634
00:30:17,020 --> 00:30:17,860
Chen Hui,

635
00:30:18,460 --> 00:30:20,020
from now on, let's call it

636
00:30:20,020 --> 00:30:21,660
the Light of Hope, okay?

637
00:30:21,660 --> 00:30:23,180
The Light of Hope?

638
00:30:24,380 --> 00:30:25,220
Okay.

639
00:30:25,820 --> 00:30:28,140
You will have
the college entrance exam next year.

640
00:30:28,140 --> 00:30:29,860
What school do you want to go to?

641
00:30:31,460 --> 00:30:32,740
What school?

642
00:30:32,740 --> 00:30:33,700
Whatever.

643
00:30:33,700 --> 00:30:34,700
Anyway,

644
00:30:34,700 --> 00:30:36,180
it has to be far away from my dad.

645
00:30:36,180 --> 00:30:37,420
Then go to Haicheng.

646
00:30:38,160 --> 00:30:39,020
Okay.

647
00:30:39,020 --> 00:30:39,860
Haicheng it is.

648
00:30:40,620 --> 00:30:43,180
I'm going to Haicheng!

649
00:30:44,460 --> 00:30:47,460
I'm going to Haicheng too!

650
00:30:47,460 --> 00:30:48,580
You two, get down from there!

651
00:30:48,580 --> 00:30:49,540
You little brats!

652
00:30:49,540 --> 00:30:50,660
Haicheng?

653
00:30:50,660 --> 00:30:51,900
I'll make sure you never leave Fengyang!

654
00:30:51,900 --> 00:30:52,740
What do we do?

655
00:30:52,740 --> 00:30:53,580
We've been caught.

656
00:30:55,540 --> 00:30:57,060
I'm going to take Songge

657
00:30:57,060 --> 00:31:00,540
to the ends of the earth!

658
00:31:00,540 --> 00:31:04,070
To the ends of the earth!

659
00:31:04,070 --> 00:31:07,100
♪Back then, the distance was in sight♪

660
00:31:07,500 --> 00:31:10,250
♪The road had no end♪

661
00:31:10,480 --> 00:31:13,330
♪Say "see you tomorrow"♪

662
00:31:13,430 --> 00:31:18,500
♪And there would surely be a future♪

663
00:31:19,180 --> 00:31:22,020
(Advanced Unit)

664
00:31:22,020 --> 00:31:23,860
(Fengyang Town Police Station,
Jiangbin Municipal PSB)

665
00:31:23,940 --> 00:31:24,780
Don't worry.

666
00:31:24,800 --> 00:31:26,780
- We'll work with the local station.
- Chief Liu.

667
00:31:27,300 --> 00:31:28,140
Okay.

668
00:31:29,010 --> 00:31:30,060
What is it, Director Chen?

669
00:31:30,070 --> 00:31:31,620
Chief Liu, I need to check in with you.

670
00:31:34,540 --> 00:31:36,300
Chief Liu, here's the thing.

671
00:31:36,300 --> 00:31:37,340
This time,

672
00:31:37,340 --> 00:31:38,500
we arrested 26 people

673
00:31:38,500 --> 00:31:40,180
who tested positive for Kejianin.

674
00:31:40,980 --> 00:31:42,860
These people are all buyers.

675
00:31:42,860 --> 00:31:44,340
And they all bought their supply

676
00:31:44,340 --> 00:31:45,340
from that missing person,

677
00:31:45,340 --> 00:31:46,660
Lu Yuan.

678
00:31:46,660 --> 00:31:47,940
Two of the sellers

679
00:31:47,940 --> 00:31:49,060
lived in the village.

680
00:31:49,060 --> 00:31:49,900
I had Limin

681
00:31:49,900 --> 00:31:50,900
take his men

682
00:31:50,900 --> 00:31:52,420
to make the arrests overnight.

683
00:31:52,420 --> 00:31:54,700
But when they got there, they found

684
00:31:54,700 --> 00:31:55,580
they had all fled.

685
00:31:57,220 --> 00:31:58,660
Both sellers ran away?

686
00:31:58,660 --> 00:31:59,620
Yes.

687
00:31:59,620 --> 00:32:00,540
The villagers said

688
00:32:00,540 --> 00:32:01,740
they've been gone for two days.

689
00:32:01,740 --> 00:32:03,140
They vanished the same day as Lu Yuan.

690
00:32:03,140 --> 00:32:04,620
They are slippery.

691
00:32:05,250 --> 00:32:06,220
Of the buyers we caught,

692
00:32:06,220 --> 00:32:07,900
has anyone seen the original bottles?

693
00:32:07,900 --> 00:32:09,220
That's the strange part.

694
00:32:09,220 --> 00:32:10,080
Among so many people,

695
00:32:10,080 --> 00:32:13,100
no one has seen the bottle
for this cough syrup.

696
00:32:13,100 --> 00:32:14,220
(Contraband, Peidun Cough Syrup)

697
00:32:15,300 --> 00:32:16,460
That is strange.

698
00:32:16,620 --> 00:32:17,760
We arrested all those people,

699
00:32:17,760 --> 00:32:18,700
yet not a single seller

700
00:32:18,700 --> 00:32:19,940
was from the town.

701
00:32:20,320 --> 00:32:22,860
And the buyers all drank
refilled cough syrup.

702
00:32:22,860 --> 00:32:24,980
No one has seen the original bottles.

703
00:32:25,740 --> 00:32:27,660
This ring is tightly organized.

704
00:32:27,660 --> 00:32:28,980
Chief Liu, does the municipal PSB

705
00:32:28,980 --> 00:32:30,460
have any new findings?

706
00:32:30,460 --> 00:32:32,020
Regarding the commemorative coin
from the scene,

707
00:32:32,020 --> 00:32:34,420
the municipal PSB conducted
a city-wide investigation.

708
00:32:34,420 --> 00:32:36,020
Only one set remains unaccounted for.

709
00:32:36,240 --> 00:32:38,340
The applicant is the owner
of a motorcycle shop.

710
00:32:38,340 --> 00:32:39,540
On the afternoon of October 1,

711
00:32:39,540 --> 00:32:41,300
he used this set
of commemorative coins as a prize

712
00:32:41,300 --> 00:32:42,600
for a lucky draw at his shop.

713
00:32:43,260 --> 00:32:44,700
They were won by a middle-aged woman.

714
00:32:44,700 --> 00:32:46,010
Her specific identity is unknown.

715
00:32:46,220 --> 00:32:47,180
A middle-aged woman?

716
00:32:48,620 --> 00:32:49,940
Aren't there way too many of them?

717
00:32:51,720 --> 00:32:53,540
Right, did you check
the potassium permanganate?

718
00:32:53,540 --> 00:32:54,500
Aside

719
00:32:54,500 --> 00:32:55,420
from medical use,

720
00:32:55,420 --> 00:32:56,980
(Potassium Permanganate, Glycerol)
it's generally a daily item

721
00:32:56,980 --> 00:32:57,980
for women.

722
00:32:57,980 --> 00:32:59,420
With retail sales like this,

723
00:32:59,420 --> 00:33:00,700
it's very hard to track.

724
00:33:04,460 --> 00:33:06,500
Let's keep investigating
the cough syrup then.

725
00:33:06,500 --> 00:33:08,260
As long as we find one seller,

726
00:33:08,260 --> 00:33:10,060
we can smoke out the whole ring.

727
00:33:10,060 --> 00:33:11,100
Whatever you say.

728
00:33:11,100 --> 00:33:12,220
Let's move.

729
00:33:13,120 --> 00:33:14,620
The municipal PSB
is taking the discovery

730
00:33:14,620 --> 00:33:15,740
of Peidun Cough Syrup in Fengyang Town

731
00:33:15,740 --> 00:33:17,580
very seriously
as it's a prohibited drug.

732
00:33:17,600 --> 00:33:19,700
This is also the first time
it's been found in our province.

733
00:33:19,700 --> 00:33:21,140
Now, this cough syrup matter

734
00:33:21,140 --> 00:33:23,680
is also closely related to
the Beimianling body-burning homicide.

735
00:33:23,690 --> 00:33:25,290
So the municipal PSB
is preparing to launch

736
00:33:25,300 --> 00:33:26,660
a major crackdown and night inspection

737
00:33:26,660 --> 00:33:28,820
against Peidun Cough Syrup in Fengyang.

738
00:33:28,820 --> 00:33:30,940
It will mainly target
public consumer venues,

739
00:33:30,940 --> 00:33:32,060
such as video halls,

740
00:33:32,060 --> 00:33:33,180
arcades,

741
00:33:33,180 --> 00:33:35,220
roller skating rinks, and dance halls.

742
00:33:35,220 --> 00:33:36,500
Whenever anyone is found

743
00:33:36,500 --> 00:33:38,260
testing positive for Kejianin
during this operation,

744
00:33:38,260 --> 00:33:40,140
interrogate them immediately
for the seller's whereabouts

745
00:33:40,140 --> 00:33:41,100
and make the arrests.

746
00:33:42,180 --> 00:33:43,300
In our Fengyang,

747
00:33:43,300 --> 00:33:44,860
there are quite a lot of places,

748
00:33:44,860 --> 00:33:45,900
large and small.

749
00:33:46,260 --> 00:33:47,740
But in our entire station,

750
00:33:47,740 --> 00:33:49,460
there are only about 20 people.

751
00:33:49,460 --> 00:33:50,860
Even if we deploy everyone,

752
00:33:50,860 --> 00:33:52,300
I'm afraid we won't have enough hands.

753
00:33:52,300 --> 00:33:54,100
The municipal PSB has notified
the Criminal Police Squad One.

754
00:33:54,100 --> 00:33:55,140
They will come to assist us

755
00:33:55,140 --> 00:33:56,460
in carrying out this operation together.

756
00:33:56,460 --> 00:33:57,820
That's great.

757
00:33:57,820 --> 00:33:59,160
With the assistance
of the municipal PSB,

758
00:33:59,160 --> 00:34:01,300
we will solve the case
as soon as possible.

759
00:34:04,020 --> 00:34:04,860
Director Chen.

760
00:34:12,540 --> 00:34:13,530
Sir.

761
00:34:13,540 --> 00:34:14,380
Who are you?

762
00:34:14,380 --> 00:34:15,260
My name is Xin Yu.

763
00:34:15,260 --> 00:34:16,420
My friend's name is Wang Sui.

764
00:34:16,420 --> 00:34:17,620
She was arrested by you yesterday.

765
00:34:17,620 --> 00:34:18,780
She's innocent.

766
00:34:20,620 --> 00:34:21,460
Who wronged her?

767
00:34:22,100 --> 00:34:23,740
She was arrested despite doing nothing.

768
00:34:23,740 --> 00:34:24,700
Doing nothing?

769
00:34:25,740 --> 00:34:27,610
That's illegal consumption
of prohibited drugs.

770
00:34:28,380 --> 00:34:29,410
She has to pay a fine

771
00:34:29,720 --> 00:34:31,140
and stay in detention for five days.

772
00:34:31,140 --> 00:34:31,980
Do you understand?

773
00:34:31,980 --> 00:34:33,420
She couldn't have taken it on purpose.

774
00:34:33,420 --> 00:34:34,780
Someone must have drugged her.

775
00:34:34,780 --> 00:34:36,260
Please be flexible.

776
00:34:36,260 --> 00:34:37,220
Don't detain her.

777
00:34:37,220 --> 00:34:39,460
Everyone says it wasn't on purpose.

778
00:34:39,460 --> 00:34:40,580
Who forced her?

779
00:34:40,580 --> 00:34:42,180
Wang Sui is a college student.

780
00:34:42,180 --> 00:34:44,060
She just came to Fengyang to visit me.

781
00:34:44,060 --> 00:34:45,060
If you detain her,

782
00:34:45,060 --> 00:34:47,420
the school will expel her
if they find out.

783
00:34:47,740 --> 00:34:49,060
She has always been a good girl.

784
00:34:49,060 --> 00:34:50,500
She wouldn't take it intentionally.

785
00:34:50,740 --> 00:34:52,340
Please don't detain her.

786
00:34:53,120 --> 00:34:54,620
I'll look into the situation further.

787
00:34:57,180 --> 00:34:58,180
(Yingxiong Roller Skating Rink)
Hui, you're back.

788
00:34:58,180 --> 00:34:59,140
- Mr. Wang.
- Mr. Wang.

789
00:35:07,140 --> 00:35:08,060
What's wrong?

790
00:35:08,820 --> 00:35:09,740
Lu Yuan is over there.

791
00:35:13,780 --> 00:35:15,180
He found this place so quickly?

792
00:35:15,500 --> 00:35:16,460
What should we do?

793
00:35:17,140 --> 00:35:18,740
Should we hide for a bit?

794
00:35:20,660 --> 00:35:22,140
We can run, but we can't hide forever.

795
00:35:23,940 --> 00:35:25,540
Let's go ask him what he wants.

796
00:35:26,340 --> 00:35:27,220
Let's go.

797
00:36:03,020 --> 00:36:04,980
(Yingxiong Roller Skating Rink)

798
00:36:13,340 --> 00:36:14,980
(Jackpot is Coming,
China Welfare Lottery)

799
00:36:14,980 --> 00:36:16,260
- Morning, Cai.
- Morning.

800
00:36:16,260 --> 00:36:17,420
Want some steamed buns?

801
00:36:17,420 --> 00:36:18,260
No, thanks.

802
00:36:23,460 --> 00:36:24,540
Why are you sleeping here?

803
00:36:26,820 --> 00:36:28,340
Something came up, so I got back late.

804
00:36:28,340 --> 00:36:30,300
You could have at least called.

805
00:36:30,300 --> 00:36:31,940
Don't you know I was worried?

806
00:36:33,950 --> 00:36:35,500
I'm going back to sleep for a bit, Mom.

807
00:36:37,700 --> 00:36:38,660
Where's Sui?

808
00:36:39,140 --> 00:36:40,660
Why didn't she come back with you?

809
00:36:43,300 --> 00:36:45,900
Sui went to sleep at a hotel.

810
00:36:45,900 --> 00:36:47,660
Why go to a hotel?

811
00:36:47,660 --> 00:36:48,500
Yesterday,

812
00:36:48,500 --> 00:36:50,420
she had a bit to drink and got sleepy.

813
00:36:50,420 --> 00:36:52,380
I told her to come back,
but she didn't want to disturb you.

814
00:36:52,380 --> 00:36:53,500
So I just took her to a hotel.

815
00:36:54,420 --> 00:36:55,620
Listen.

816
00:36:55,620 --> 00:36:57,220
Sui is a good kid.

817
00:36:57,220 --> 00:36:58,900
Don't you go corrupting her.

818
00:36:59,580 --> 00:37:01,180
I know.

819
00:37:01,180 --> 00:37:02,100
Cai.

820
00:37:03,340 --> 00:37:04,780
Hey, little beauty.

821
00:37:04,780 --> 00:37:05,780
Why so early?

822
00:37:06,260 --> 00:37:08,140
Give me

823
00:37:08,140 --> 00:37:09,540
two lottery tickets.

824
00:37:10,300 --> 00:37:11,500
Sure.

825
00:37:11,500 --> 00:37:12,740
How's business been

826
00:37:12,740 --> 00:37:14,940
at your roller skating rink lately?

827
00:37:14,940 --> 00:37:15,860
It's been pretty good.

828
00:37:17,060 --> 00:37:18,780
Good luck.

829
00:37:20,940 --> 00:37:22,060
Mom, I'm heading back now.

830
00:37:25,020 --> 00:37:26,170
Han Ning, wait a second.

831
00:37:28,860 --> 00:37:29,700
Yeah?

832
00:37:29,840 --> 00:37:30,700
I

833
00:37:30,700 --> 00:37:31,860
remember you saying

834
00:37:32,700 --> 00:37:34,020
your boss's father

835
00:37:34,020 --> 00:37:36,060
works at the police station, right?

836
00:37:36,060 --> 00:37:37,060
Yeah.

837
00:37:37,060 --> 00:37:38,540
He's the Deputy Director.

838
00:37:38,540 --> 00:37:39,900
Could I ask him for a favor?

839
00:37:40,420 --> 00:37:41,460
What is it?

840
00:37:58,100 --> 00:38:01,860
(Menu)

841
00:38:03,660 --> 00:38:04,780
This is my boss.

842
00:38:05,300 --> 00:38:06,380
Boss,

843
00:38:07,180 --> 00:38:08,820
this is a neighbor of mine.

844
00:38:08,820 --> 00:38:10,260
Her name is Xin Yu.

845
00:38:10,260 --> 00:38:11,900
You're the one
who sings at the club, right?

846
00:38:11,900 --> 00:38:13,900
That's right. Do you go there often?

847
00:38:13,900 --> 00:38:15,540
Not often. Just occasionally.

848
00:38:15,540 --> 00:38:16,740
Next time you come, look for me.

849
00:38:16,740 --> 00:38:17,700
Drinks are on me.

850
00:38:22,180 --> 00:38:23,020
Boss,

851
00:38:23,780 --> 00:38:26,460
she said she has something
to discuss with you.

852
00:38:26,460 --> 00:38:27,580
Why don't you two talk?

853
00:38:27,580 --> 00:38:28,820
I'll head out first.

854
00:38:33,140 --> 00:38:33,980
Go ahead.

855
00:38:35,740 --> 00:38:38,460
I heard your father is the Director
of the police station.

856
00:38:39,180 --> 00:38:40,340
Deputy.

857
00:38:40,340 --> 00:38:41,900
Is that why you're looking for me?

858
00:38:41,900 --> 00:38:42,740
Here is the thing.

859
00:38:42,740 --> 00:38:44,900
A friend of mine was arrested
by the police yesterday.

860
00:38:44,900 --> 00:38:46,100
She might even be detained.

861
00:38:46,100 --> 00:38:47,500
Then you've got the wrong person.

862
00:38:47,500 --> 00:38:48,940
Never mind your friend,

863
00:38:48,940 --> 00:38:50,220
even if I were arrested,

864
00:38:50,220 --> 00:38:51,460
he wouldn't lift a finger.

865
00:38:51,460 --> 00:38:53,060
But she was framed.

866
00:38:53,060 --> 00:38:55,180
She just got to Fengyang,
and she's still in university.

867
00:38:55,180 --> 00:38:56,660
She just came to the dance hall
that day to see me.

868
00:38:56,660 --> 00:38:58,510
She must have drunk something
she shouldn't have.

869
00:38:59,620 --> 00:39:00,900
If she really gets detained,

870
00:39:00,900 --> 00:39:03,180
and if her parents find out,
it'll worry them to death.

871
00:39:03,180 --> 00:39:04,140
And

872
00:39:04,140 --> 00:39:06,180
if the school finds out, it's over.

873
00:39:06,180 --> 00:39:08,010
She won't even be able
to finish her studies.

874
00:39:09,300 --> 00:39:11,180
(Yingxiong Roller Skating Rink)

875
00:39:15,620 --> 00:39:17,260
I haven't finished yet.

876
00:39:17,260 --> 00:39:18,700
Regarding my friend's situation...

877
00:39:18,700 --> 00:39:20,260
I have a friend here. We'll talk later.

878
00:39:20,260 --> 00:39:21,380
Mr. Huo.

879
00:39:22,540 --> 00:39:24,060
What brings you here today?

880
00:39:25,700 --> 00:39:27,140
I have some business with Chen Hui.

881
00:39:27,620 --> 00:39:29,020
- Mr. Huo.
- You get back to work.

882
00:39:29,980 --> 00:39:31,340
Let's talk inside. Come.

883
00:39:40,340 --> 00:39:41,580
Mr. Huo,

884
00:39:41,580 --> 00:39:42,620
what are you doing here?

885
00:39:44,620 --> 00:39:46,260
How is the search

886
00:39:46,260 --> 00:39:47,380
for Jiao Yuqin going?

887
00:39:48,020 --> 00:39:49,940
I've already asked everyone under me.

888
00:39:49,940 --> 00:39:51,300
Nobody knows Jiao Yuqin.

889
00:39:51,300 --> 00:39:52,740
You have to give me some time.

890
00:39:52,740 --> 00:39:53,660
I don't have time to give you.

891
00:39:53,660 --> 00:39:54,860
Hurry up and find her for me.

892
00:39:54,860 --> 00:39:55,780
Mr. Huo,

893
00:39:55,780 --> 00:39:57,060
let's be reasonable here.

894
00:39:57,060 --> 00:39:57,980
You only gave me a name

895
00:39:57,980 --> 00:39:59,180
and one day.

896
00:39:59,180 --> 00:40:00,900
Where am I supposed
to find someone that fast?

897
00:40:01,540 --> 00:40:03,020
Do you have any other information?

898
00:40:15,300 --> 00:40:16,140
You know her, right?

899
00:40:17,500 --> 00:40:18,420
Mr. Huo,

900
00:40:19,100 --> 00:40:20,740
I swear I really don't know her.

901
00:40:20,740 --> 00:40:22,060
Who are you kidding?

902
00:40:22,900 --> 00:40:24,700
You sold her the cough syrup,

903
00:40:24,700 --> 00:40:25,700
and you don't know her?

904
00:40:25,700 --> 00:40:27,380
I really don't.

905
00:40:27,380 --> 00:40:29,140
I just supply the drug to the dealers.

906
00:40:29,140 --> 00:40:31,220
How would I know who they sell it to?

907
00:40:31,220 --> 00:40:32,180
Bring your dealers here.

908
00:40:32,180 --> 00:40:33,070
I'll ask them myself.

909
00:40:33,980 --> 00:40:36,020
I can't contact my dealers.

910
00:40:36,020 --> 00:40:38,540
The police are checking
for cough syrup everywhere now.

911
00:40:38,540 --> 00:40:40,340
What if they've been caught,
and if I contact them,

912
00:40:40,340 --> 00:40:41,820
wouldn't I be turning myself in?

913
00:40:41,820 --> 00:40:42,940
I don't care about that.

914
00:40:42,940 --> 00:40:43,980
That's your problem.

915
00:40:43,980 --> 00:40:45,980
I just want you to find Jiao Yuqin.

916
00:40:45,980 --> 00:40:47,220
If you can't find her,

917
00:40:47,220 --> 00:40:48,940
I'll report you to the police station.

918
00:40:48,940 --> 00:40:50,300
Let's see how your father
deals with you then.

919
00:40:51,900 --> 00:40:53,500
I don't think you'd dare to report me.

920
00:40:59,820 --> 00:41:01,060
What do you mean?

921
00:41:02,860 --> 00:41:05,460
Aren't you afraid of the police
investigation into Beimianling?

922
00:41:05,460 --> 00:41:07,060
Did you take care

923
00:41:07,060 --> 00:41:08,600
of the potassium permanganate
in your car?

924
00:41:15,500 --> 00:41:16,540
Boy,

925
00:41:17,980 --> 00:41:19,140
are you threatening me?

926
00:41:19,620 --> 00:41:21,310
You want to go down together,
is that it?

927
00:41:23,340 --> 00:41:24,180
Mr. Huo,

928
00:41:24,860 --> 00:41:26,140
I gave you my word.

929
00:41:26,140 --> 00:41:27,900
So I'll find her for you.

930
00:41:27,900 --> 00:41:29,500
But you have to give me some time.

931
00:41:30,540 --> 00:41:32,220
Besides, in all of Fengyang,

932
00:41:32,220 --> 00:41:33,910
I'm the only one
who can help you find her.

933
00:41:37,300 --> 00:41:38,380
I'll trust you this once.

934
00:41:45,140 --> 00:41:46,180
Mr. Huo, are you leaving?

935
00:41:46,740 --> 00:41:47,740
Take care.

936
00:41:47,740 --> 00:41:48,580
Take care, Mr. Huo.

937
00:41:52,380 --> 00:41:54,060
What's going on with you and Mr. Huo?

938
00:41:54,060 --> 00:41:56,100
Why did you have
to talk in the warehouse?

939
00:41:56,100 --> 00:41:57,300
It's nothing.

940
00:41:57,300 --> 00:41:59,100
Remember when he and I
took you to the hospital?

941
00:41:59,100 --> 00:42:00,940
I broke his trunk latch.

942
00:42:00,940 --> 00:42:02,860
I promised to pay him back.

943
00:42:02,860 --> 00:42:03,980
It's all settled now.

944
00:42:04,020 --> 00:42:06,700
(Yingxiong Roller Skating Rink)

945
00:42:15,620 --> 00:42:16,900
The one in the blue clothes.

946
00:42:16,900 --> 00:42:17,860
I'm talking to you.

947
00:42:17,860 --> 00:42:19,420
Yeah, you. Come here.

948
00:42:19,420 --> 00:42:20,340
Go, quick.

949
00:42:21,500 --> 00:42:23,100
Everyone, move inside.

950
00:42:23,100 --> 00:42:24,500
Police inspection!

951
00:42:24,500 --> 00:42:26,580
Turn on the lights. Turn off the music.

952
00:42:26,580 --> 00:42:27,740
Stop.

953
00:42:27,740 --> 00:42:28,780
Over here.

954
00:42:28,780 --> 00:42:30,260
Men in one line, women in another.

955
00:42:30,260 --> 00:42:31,140
Line up.

956
00:42:31,140 --> 00:42:33,220
Li, take him.

957
00:42:33,220 --> 00:42:34,620
Get him sorted out.

958
00:42:34,620 --> 00:42:36,100
Move.

959
00:42:36,100 --> 00:42:38,020
Men's line here, women's line there.

960
00:42:38,020 --> 00:42:39,460
Spot check.

961
00:42:39,460 --> 00:42:40,300
Take a paper cup.

962
00:42:40,300 --> 00:42:41,260
You're doing urine tests in a moment.

963
00:42:41,260 --> 00:42:42,100
Hurry up.

964
00:42:42,100 --> 00:42:43,420
Men in one line, women in another.

965
00:42:43,420 --> 00:42:44,580
Hurry up.

966
00:42:45,900 --> 00:42:48,060
Police inspection. Line up.

967
00:43:03,190 --> 00:43:09,310
♪I always thought
once we see the full picture♪

968
00:43:10,630 --> 00:43:16,430
♪We could understand
each other with empathy♪

969
00:43:18,030 --> 00:43:24,470
♪I always thought
the path we never took♪

970
00:43:25,190 --> 00:43:30,790
♪Must have had more beautiful scenery♪

971
00:43:32,630 --> 00:43:35,990
♪Keep moving forward
and don't look back♪

972
00:43:36,350 --> 00:43:39,590
♪The shore is only reached
by the road ahead♪

973
00:43:39,990 --> 00:43:42,830
♪Too much debt has accumulated♪

974
00:43:43,750 --> 00:43:46,630
♪In this short life♪

975
00:43:47,390 --> 00:43:51,070
♪Between right and wrong,
how to choose♪

976
00:43:51,150 --> 00:43:54,630
♪Regret is inevitable in the end♪

977
00:43:54,790 --> 00:44:01,430
♪Even so-called love
is repaid with pain♪

978
00:44:01,910 --> 00:44:05,870
♪I hear the laughter
and follow the crowd♪

979
00:44:06,070 --> 00:44:09,270
♪Into the streets and alleys♪

980
00:44:09,550 --> 00:44:16,390
♪On that brightly lit night♪

981
00:44:17,110 --> 00:44:20,670
♪Unfortunately, the breeze in town♪

982
00:44:20,870 --> 00:44:24,390
♪Can no longer catch up to the children♪

983
00:44:24,390 --> 00:44:27,550
♪Times have changed♪

984
00:44:27,950 --> 00:44:30,350
♪Now, everything♪

985
00:44:31,030 --> 00:44:35,190
♪Is no longer what it used to be♪

